title: World Time Attack Challenge secured for Western Sydney (Destination NSW)
text: ( Source : Destination NSW ) The World Time Attack Challenge , a time trial and motoring festival featuring some of the world's fastest cars, will hit Western Sydney next week as the NSW Government announced the event will remain at Sydney
